title: About
text:
We are a group of four students of Sciences Po Paris in the Master of Research in Economics, and this Website aims to help us present our work for the Microeconomics 2 class. We received a grade of 14 over 20.

title: Microeconomics 2 project website
text:
Hello, we are a four students of the Master of Research in Economics of Sciences Po, and this is the website of the work we submitted for our Microeconomics 2 class, focused on a game theoretical approach of pollution taxation. We received a grade of 14 over 20.
